        "content_html": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0225/15/00/a37a5098782945d5be49ac98fc14ac02_1260_12931_8157503.0x0.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0224/13/30/633bbb8bdbc043aba5fc0c44d5c83eea_1074_1820_1295709.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1085\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">声动淮水·乐聚颍州<br>春风渡淮水，音符跃暖城<br>3月21日起，斑马精酿 × QQ音乐 联袂巨献</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">巅峰之约，共赴阜阳春日乐章！<br>持续解锁阜阳多日音乐盛宴，敬请期待...<br>📍 地点：安徽省阜阳市斑马音乐节草坪</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0226/10/00/fd3c25b5031e4635a8ab5319b3f0ea9f_1274_2155_2275635.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0226/10/00/bb96c9c72b3e4bce996283dba406fba8_540_9099_5335195.0x0.png?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\"></p>"
